S.FORM: == kakiliman == An-man "A-la-pow a kamu, عمانmasaluma, 'Ammān,(ʕamːaːn)" nu Si-ya a kanatal Ya-tan angangan atu satabakiay a tukay, nuyniay kanatal a kezay, cen-ce atu pulung nu lalangawan, katukuh 2021 a mihcaan, 4,061,150, ku tademaw nu An-man, u satabakiay a tukay nu Li-ban a kakitizaan, A-la-pow i kitakit u sakalima nu tabakiay a tukuy atu sawalian a kakitizaan nu sakasiwa tabakiay a kakitizaan. tukuy tiin i nuwamisan nuyni a kanatal, satipan nu A-ci-lun a buyubuyu'an. kitizaan a ngangan nu An-man makayniay nicalapan a buyu' nu heni "Jabal" anucaay diheb "Wadi", saayaway a katahkalan taneng pasuzikuz katukuh kung-yen8 a se-ci, tiza nipanganganan a An-ca-le nazipaan nu baluhay ba'tuay a ziday, itiza tahkal ku kitakitay nu kasumamaday nitu'tu'an ci An-ca-le tu masatademaway. i nu mukin a ziday, uyni a tukay pangangan han tu Rabbath Ammon, kilul i likisian nakatuud ku masasumaay mikuwan, pasu angangan a tukay nu Ya-men hungti a kanatal. kung-yen 3 se-ci,Tow-le-mi hungti a zidayay a Ay-ci atu ba-law Tow-le-mi al-se muliyaw patizeng tuyni a tukuay, pasumad tu ngangan "bey-la-tye-bey" han, malakitizaan nu lalangawan nu Si-la. i pikuwanan nu Low-ma, bey-la-tye-bey na u Te-ka-pow-li-say nu sabaw cacay a tukay nu Si-la-low-ma, sakuwan nu Pey-te-la-a-la-pow. kung-yen 7 se-ci, cen-tung Ha-li-ba makay sawali Low-ma mademec tu kuyni a tukay, sumad hantu ku ngangan An-man han. . i hamin teban nu se-ci tu hamin nu demiad, uyni a tukay malu tungus nu Pa-al-ka-kaw-ti, pakaniya'ay tu cacanan kacakat atu kapakuyuc a mihcaan. katukuh tu 15 se-ci katukuh 1878 a mihcaan, mapaales tu ku An-man, itawya uyni a kitizaan uyza dada' Ciy-al ke-s ku mana'nelay. ayzaay tu a ziday, An-man a saayaway se-cen-bu-wi-yen-huy 1909 a mihcaan patizeng, yu An-man i 1921 a mihcaan mapatuzu' u likut a Ye-tan a angangnan nu tukay hawsa, uyni a tukay pakaniya'ay tu kalamkam macakat, misulup tu makaniay Ye-tan atu Li-ban-te masasumaay a tukay nu mabulaway, apakaniya'ay tu pina kalalid nu mabulaway, saayaway patizeng tu pitu adidi'ay byu' a tukay. imahini maawas t uku 19 adidi'ay abuyu', masanga' pasu 22 ku pikawawan a tuse nu An-man, imahinisawali a An-man angangan amisuped tu canacanan tu nazipaan nu likisi, hina palekal mikawaw tu lalangawan, satipay An-man nu ayzaaytu a mihcaan, nuyni a tukuy angangan nu kezay. ayza, An-man nu cung-tung a kitizaan cayay kakatuuday a I-s-lan-cyaw, kilisetu atu cayay kakatuud a singku caay kahapinang ku kacatuli a mapulung mueneng tuyni a lalaan' 2018 a mihcaan pakala tu 100 emang ku midangay a labang katukuh i An-man, uyni An-man malahamin nu kitakit tu saka 89 ku mipalitaay tu satabakiay a tukay atu saka12 ku mipalitaay nu satabakiay a tukay nu A-la-pow. An-man a kezay dadawa a macakat, duduc hamin nu kitakit atu kitakitay a tukay nu migingkiway tu wanglu "GaWC" nihapuan a "kitakitay a tukay" a nganganan, An-man tungusay Beta caay ku nu kanatalay tukay dada', duduc tukay a kezay, mikuliay, hekal atu syakay lalangawan a kahini, mapasakamu Cung-tung atu pey-bey u sakapahay a tukay. imahini An-man nu A-la-pow kitakit u sakanamuhan miawasay a kanatal a kusi patizeng tu kitizaay mikawaw, atu masilac tu Tu-ha, Tu-pay dada'. 中文為維基百科 : 安曼

== kakiliman == An-man "A-la-pow a kamo, عمانmasaloma, 'Ammān,(ʕamːaːn)" no Si-ya a kanatal Ya-tan angangan ato satabakiay a tokay, noyniay kanatal a kezay, cen-ce ato polong no lalangawan, katokoh 2021 a mihcaan, 4,061,150, ko tademaw no An-man, o satabakiay a tokay no Li-ban a kakitizaan, A-la-pow i kitakit o sakalima no tabakiay a tokoy ato sawalian a kakitizaan no sakasiwa tabakiay a kakitizaan. tokoy tiin i nowamisan noyni a kanatal, satipan no A-ci-lon a boyoboyo'an. kitizaan a ngangan no An-man makayniay nicalapan a boyo' no heni "Jabal" anocaay diheb "Wadi", saayaway a katahkalan taneng pasozikoz katokoh kong-yen8 a se-ci, tiza nipanganganan a An-ca-le nazipaan no balohay ba'toay a ziday, itiza tahkal ko kitakitay no kasomamaday nito'to'an ci An-ca-le to masatademaway. i no mokin a ziday, oyni a tokay pangangan han to Rabbath Ammon, kilol i likisian nakatood ko masasomaay mikowan, paso angangan a tokay no Ya-men hongti a kanatal. kong-yen 3 somad hanto ko ngangan An-man han. . i hamin teban no se-ci to hamin no demiad, oyni a tokay malo tongos no Pa-al-ka-kaw-ti, pakaniya'ay to cacanan kacakat ato kapakoyoc a mihcaan. katokoh to 15 se-ci katokoh 1878 a mihcaan, mapaales to ko An-man, itawya oyni a kitizaan oyza dada' Ciy-al ke-s ko mana'nelay. ayzaay to a ziday, An-man a saayaway se-cen-bo-wi-yen-hoy 1909 a mihcaan patizeng, yo An-man apakaniya'ay to pina kalalid no mabolaway, saayaway patizeng to pito adidi'ay byo' a tokay. imahini maawas t oko 19 adidi'ay aboyo', masanga' paso 22 ko pikawawan a tose no An-man, imahinisawali a kitizaan cayay kakatooday a I-s-lan-cyaw, kiliseto ato cayay kakatood a singko caay kahapinang ko kacatoli a mapolong moeneng toyni a lalaan' 2018 a mihcaan pakala to 100 emang ko midangay a labang An-man a kezay dadawa a macakat, dodoc hamin no kitakit ato kitakitay a tokay no migingkiway to wanglo "GaWC" nihapoan a "kitakitay a tokay" a nganganan, An-man tongosay Beta caay ko no kanatalay tokay dada', dodoc tokay a kezay, mikoliay, hekal ato syakay lalangawan a kahini, mapasakamo Cong-tong ato pey-bey o sakapahay a tokay. imahini An-man no A-la-pow kitakit o sakanamohan miawasay a kanatal a kosi patizeng to kitizaay mikawaw, ato masilac to To-ha, To-pay dada'. 中文為維基百科 : 安曼
